data.description: Beautiful lake home with huge deck looking over Lake Sequoia that also connects to Lake Thunderbird on a dead end street. This home is a spacious remodeled 3br 3b home with modern finishes and a brand new roof!!! Upstairs is a large guest room with a walk in closest and a large private bathroom along with a large living area and updated kitchen. The master bedroom is also upstairs and has a beautiful view of the lake with 2 sliding doors. Down stairs is a large finished basement that includes a full bath and W/D. Down stairs also has a large glass sliding door with a great view of the lake. The back yard includes a large dock along with a gazebo that has also been remolded and has a new roof.
